# Day 36 – Cognitive Pattern Explorer using Claude AI

## Objective

Built an interactive Cognitive Pattern Explorer to understand different thinking tendencies through guided scenarios and reflection activities.

## Features

- Calm Mode & Stress Mode
- Interactive Thinking Scenarios
- Drag-and-Drop Priority Cards
- Thinking Timeline Activity
- Personalized Reflection Journal
- Thinking Pattern Breakdown
- Progress Tracker
- Responsive Design
- Replay Functionality

## Tech Stack

- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

## Key Learnings

- Different situations influence decision-making styles.
- Reflection improves self-awareness and critical thinking.
- Interactive applications make learning more engaging.
- AI can support educational experiences without making personal assessments.

